column5: Stopped at a few spots.  The MAD         Notty at Angus      Mouth of the Pine
Brian.. You shoud really go for a.quick tour and.check out minnesing swamp and edenville. Ive never seen so much water their!
I have friends with farms bordering the swamp.  They have lived there for 60 yeas and have never seen water like this before.  Many roads are under 3' of water...  It's like a massive lake...
It's no Lake Algonquin but it does remind one of a Jonny Cash song.

Brian.. You shoud really go for a.quick tour and.check out minnesing swamp and edenville. Ive never seen so much water their!  I drove over the Notty on the way home from OS yesterday..  You can't even see where the river ends and the farmers fields start!!  Insane!!!
